    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The terrorist appear ready to trade with the bandits.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The goblin recognises the terrorists as the priests of the church.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The gunwitch has a short crisis and the Goblin makes fun of her.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The terrorists ask the bandit leader what is he doing with a goblin among
      them.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: Leaving security to a green ape is stupid.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The goblin grins at them, hand in her gun.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The deal is going well when out of nowhere the guard falls off a tree nearby
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The bandit leader tells you to kill her.
